2. Use [scripting](https://www.elastic.co/guide/en/elasticsearch/reference/current/modules-scripting.html) to filter out documents:

(this script is a quick example i whipped out, you can write a more efficient version to optimize runtime, Assuming many documents wont have any of these terms you query it would be efficient to add a `query` (similar to what you&#39;ve been doing) before the `filter` action to just iterate over &quot;suspected&quot; matches.)

